<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome Email</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin:
      0; padding: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content:
      center; height: 100vh; } .email-container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius:
      8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .email-header {
      text-align: center; padding-bottom: 20px; } .email-header h1 { color:
      #4318a7; } .email-body { font-size: 16px; color: #333333; line-height:
      1.5; margin-bottom: 20px; } .email-body p { margin: 10px 0; } .footer {
      font-size: 14px; color: #777777; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; }
      .footer a { color: #4318a7; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Welcome, {{user.name}}!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Thank you for joining us! We're thrilled to have you on board.</p>
        <p>Get ready to explore all the exciting features we have to offer. Your
          journey towards a more amazing experience starts right here!</p>
        <p>Stay tuned for updates and feel free to reach out if you need any
          help. We're here for you!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,<br />The Coppola Team</p>
        <p><a href="#">Need help?</a> | <a href="#">Explore More</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>